# Architecture

- Keep native shell, workspace core, plugins, terminal, LSP, and editor island as separate modules.
- Prefer small modules and explicit TEA (Model/Msg/update) state.
- Do not import VS Code workbench code into the native shell.
- WebView is allowed only for the editor island, never the whole shell.
